believes the actor will comply, but would not say when and where.
   O'Toole and Ms. O'Toole met about six years ago, but never
married. After the child was born, the mother began using O'Toole's
last name. A short time later, the couple split and have been
embroiled in a bitter custody dispute for more than a year.
